# LightRAG Response Format

When user query starts with `@lightrag ?`, format the final answer exactly with these sections:

1. `–Ъ–Њ—А–Њ—В–Ї–Є–є –Њ—В–≤–µ—В`
2. `–І—В–Њ –љ–∞–є–і–µ–љ–Њ –≤ –С–Ч`
3. `–£—А–Њ–≤–µ–љ—М —Г–≤–µ—А–µ–љ–љ–Њ—Б—В–Є`

Output rules:

- Keep total response concise.
- In `–Ъ–Њ—А–Њ—В–Ї–Є–є –Њ—В–≤–µ—В`: 1-3 lines with direct answer.
- In `–І—В–Њ –љ–∞–є–і–µ–љ–Њ –≤ –С–Ч`: 2-5 bullets with concrete facts from MCP results.
- In `–£—А–Њ–≤–µ–љ—М —Г–≤–µ—А–µ–љ–љ–Њ—Б—В–Є`: one of `–Т—Л—Б–Њ–Ї–Є–є` / `–°—А–µ–і–љ–Є–є` / `–Э–Є–Ј–Ї–Є–є` plus short reason.
- If MCP lookup fails, explicitly say lookup failed and set confidence to `–Э–Є–Ј–Ї–Є–є`.
